item.title: Error Connecting To Server. (VPS)
item.dc:creator: @luna-scape luna-scape
item.description:
@luna-scape wrote:

A vps is most of the time already oortforwarded.
U can try out the firewall offline.
And use the vps ip in ur new client (or you mus setup no-ip on the vps)
Check if ur port is up on canyouseeme.org
If ts still not working ak the company if they can portforward it for you

Goodluck
